notepad .gitignore
```

Click **Yes** when Notepad asks to create a new file.

Paste this inside:
```
# Frontend
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/build/
frontend/.env

# Backend
backend/target/
backend/.env
backend/*.jar

# AI Service
ai_service/__pycache__/
ai_service/venv/
ai_service/.env
ai_service/*.pyc

# General
.DS_Store
*.log


# Virtual Environment - Never upload this
ai_service/.venv/
.venv/
venv/
env/

# AI Model files - Too large for GitHub
ai_service/services/models/
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.pt
*.pth
*.onnx

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env

# Java
target/
*.class
*.jar
.idea/

# React
node_modules/
build/
dist/
.env.local

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db